data.description: This property is a stunning oasis, with approximately 2.2 acres of spacious land perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation. The property features matured palm trees adding to the overall beauty of the landscape.    The home itself is a spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bath property, with a total of 2048 square feet of living space. The interior of the home is spacious and perfect for entertainment. The stainless steel appliances in the kitchen give an upscale touch, and the fireplace adds warmth and a cozy atmosphere to the family room.    Other great features of the property include a workshop/garage for those who love to work on DIY projects, a 3 car carport providing ample parking space for residents and guests, and a storage shed for additional storage needs. The enclosed patio is perfect for lounging outdoors, enjoying a cup of coffee, and taking in the breathtaking views of the surrounding mountains.    Located just about a half mile off the paved road, this property offers privacy and serenity, while still being easily accessible. The location is also incredibly convenient, with the property being close to water and mountains, providing ample opportunities for adventure and outdoor fun.    Overall, this property is an incredible find, with everything you need to live a luxurious and relaxed lifestyle. Whether you need space for family and friends, or just some peace and quiet away from the hustle and bustle of the city, this property is the perfect place to call home.
